description:
NimiTV has released the new and fully featured iOS application for streaming Albanian TV channels. With the new NimiTV iOS app you can watch all of your favorite Albanian live TV channels and videos on demand, listen to the most popular Albanian radio and much more on the go. NimiTV offers 250+ Albanian channels, sports and movie channels, including Tring, ArtMotion and Kujtesa channels on any iOS device.

NimiTV Albanian TV app has been the leader in TV for all European clients living abroad. We now present the iOS app to give you access to all features on the go, while going to work, on the train, and anywhere else you may want! Sign Up today and let’s get started.

NimiTV Albanian TV app offers:

- Video on Demand option;

The VOD feature allows you to watch your favorite Kosovo and Albania serials, TV shows, and music programs as well as the latest Albanian movies, are at your service at any time.

- Catch-up TV option;

- Live TV from Albania;

- Listening to Albanian radios;

- NimiTV is the only TV platform that offers 24-hour call support;

- Watching TV programs on 3 devices at the same time without additional payment.
